1
00:01:45,210 --> 00:01:47,770
Hand it over!

2
00:01:50,090 --> 00:01:52,450
Is this what you wanted, Chiffon?

3
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:55,710
Yes! Thank you, Bege!

4
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:59,480
But we definitely took on a big headache!

5
00:01:59,480 --> 00:02:03,850
Honestly, getting away is now
more important than the assassination!

6
00:02:03,850 --> 00:02:05,930
What are you saying, Bege?!

7
00:02:07,060 --> 00:02:10,420
We decided to help Nami and the others
get away safely!

8
00:02:10,420 --> 00:02:14,730
We can't just give up halfway 
simply because we want to save ourselves!

9
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:18,360
This is how one repays their debt!

10
00:02:19,870 --> 00:02:21,410
Mm-hm!

11
00:02:21,410 --> 00:02:22,440
Rero !

12
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:26,640
It's going to be all right!
Believe in the taste of the cake!

13
00:02:26,640 --> 00:02:29,540
Black Leg is truly an amazing cook!

14
00:02:31,210 --> 00:02:35,000
Man! This is why I love you, Chiffon!

15
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:38,010
Madam!

16
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:42,890
Wedding cake!

17
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:46,020
Let's shake them off, guys!

18
00:02:46,020 --> 00:02:48,640
Yeah!

19
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:03,750
It's Commander Smoothie's ship!

20
00:03:03,750 --> 00:03:05,710
Commander Smoothie!

21
00:03:05,710 --> 00:03:10,040
Mistress Citron! Mistress Cinnamon!

22
00:03:16,920 --> 00:03:20,970
Are you ready, Straw Hats?

23
00:03:20,970 --> 00:03:23,270
Another fleet is on our tail!

24
00:03:23,270 --> 00:03:25,850
It's Sweet Commander Smoothie's ship!

25
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:30,330
Big Mom is gone,
but now there's a sweet commander!

26
00:03:30,330 --> 00:03:33,310
It's that woman who squeezes stuff...

27
00:03:34,070 --> 00:03:35,940
Sister Smoothie!

28
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:40,570
How much longer
until we reach Cacao Island?

29
00:03:40,580 --> 00:03:43,030
A little over three hours from now!

30
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:46,650
We'll get there at around one a.m.,
just as we promised!

31
00:03:46,650 --> 00:03:52,790
But we don't know where or when Luffy
is going to appear on Cacao Island,

32
00:03:52,790 --> 00:03:55,500
and we have no way to tell him it's dangerous!

33
00:03:59,590 --> 00:04:04,180
There's only one plan I can think of
for us to get past Cacao Island.

34
00:04:14,980 --> 00:04:19,490
Minister Oven! Our fleets are
slowly surrounding the island!

35
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:22,240
Is this really necessary?!

36
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:26,140
There's no way Commander Katakuri
will let Straw Hat escape, anyway!

37
00:04:26,140 --> 00:04:29,080
Tell that to Tamago and Mont d'Or!

38
00:04:29,080 --> 00:04:31,950
It's necessary, Big Brother Oven!

39
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:33,730
Can you believe it?!

40
00:04:33,730 --> 00:04:37,670
That big explosion of the chateau
was planned, too!

41
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:39,000
What?!

42
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:43,860
Even though they're a small group of rookies,
we cannot underestimate them!

43
00:04:43,860 --> 00:04:46,800
If they escape,
we'll be humiliated beyond repair!

44
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:50,780
Don't worry...
They won't get past us here!

45
00:04:51,730 --> 00:04:55,970
Listen! About three hours
from now, at one a.m.,

46
00:04:55,970 --> 00:05:00,940
the separated members of the Straw Hat crew
will meet up here at Cacao Island.

47
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:06,000
Think of it as your last chance
to kill them all!

48
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:07,200
Yes, sir!

49
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:14,440
If by any chance Straw Hat appears,
he'll come out of a mirror on the island!

50
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:18,060
Everyone, go and break
every mirror in this town.

51
00:05:20,670 --> 00:05:23,550
Didn't you hear me?! Just do it!

52
00:05:23,550 --> 00:05:26,010
No way! Even the precious mirrors?!

53
00:05:26,010 --> 00:05:31,260
He's an ability user. If you have a mirror
that you don't want to break, throw it into the sea.

54
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:34,480
You can retrieve it later! Anyway...

55
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:40,440
this is the only mirror
that will remain on the island!

56
00:05:44,900 --> 00:05:48,860
There must be no others!

57
00:05:48,860 --> 00:05:53,800
If anyone allows Straw Hat
to escape from one of their mirrors,

58
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:57,000
we will execute their entire family!

59
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,070
Hurry up!

60
00:05:58,830 --> 00:06:00,270
Y-Yes, sir!

61
00:06:03,960 --> 00:06:07,930
Don't think you can get away, Straw Hat!

62
00:06:07,930 --> 00:06:11,680
For you, this isn't an exit...

63
00:06:12,230 --> 00:06:14,570
it's the entrance to hell!

64
00:06:26,090 --> 00:06:28,370
My apologies...

65
00:06:28,370 --> 00:06:32,430
It was foolish of me
to not notice her needles.

66
00:06:32,430 --> 00:06:37,590
In a duel between pirates,
there's no such thing as playing dirty.

67
00:06:39,710 --> 00:06:42,630
Not being able to dodge them
was my fault!

68
00:07:08,670 --> 00:07:10,820
I no longer think...

69
00:07:10,820 --> 00:07:14,630
that you're below my level!

70
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:17,280
Is that so?! I'm glad to hear it!

71
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,980
Thanks!

72
00:07:21,520 --> 00:07:22,550
But...

73
00:07:25,730 --> 00:07:27,500
I'm gonna win!

74
00:07:29,260 --> 00:07:31,040
Ouch!

75
00:07:31,060 --> 00:07:33,550
You have no time to rest!

76
00:07:33,550 --> 00:07:36,100
If you're unable to dodge 100 times,
I won't let you eat.

77
00:07:36,100 --> 00:07:36,920
What?!

78
00:07:36,940 --> 00:07:39,440
If you think that sounds bad,
then concentrate!

79
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:47,930
I found you!

80
00:07:47,930 --> 00:07:50,050
Ouch!

81
00:07:50,050 --> 00:07:54,280
Your enemy won't always
be in front of you...

82
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:59,380
It's easy to read animals' minds
because they show all of their emotions.

83
00:07:59,380 --> 00:08:06,290
But... humans are different...
We can defy expectations and cheat others.

84
00:08:07,290 --> 00:08:09,090
"Growwwl"

85
00:08:09,100 --> 00:08:10,960
Ouch!

86
00:08:21,910 --> 00:08:24,980
I'm hungry, Rayleigh!

87
00:08:24,980 --> 00:08:29,320
Do you think your enemy
will care if you're hungry?

88
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:33,360
Every attack has an intent...

89
00:08:33,360 --> 00:08:34,270
Ow!

90
00:08:34,270 --> 00:08:36,160
and a presence!

91
00:08:40,880 --> 00:08:42,700
I smell something delicious.

92
00:08:43,300 --> 00:08:46,460
That's my dinner.
Don't pay it any mind.

93
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:53,360
There you are!

94
00:08:58,870 --> 00:08:59,760
There!

95
00:09:07,120 --> 00:09:11,700
Don't just attack blindly, Luffy!

96
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:17,110
Rayleigh, that hurts!
I can feel your anger!

97
00:09:17,110 --> 00:09:18,760
That is also haki!

98
00:09:18,760 --> 00:09:20,900
Sharpen your senses!

99
00:09:20,900 --> 00:09:22,400
Ouch!

100
00:09:22,400 --> 00:09:24,990
Feel your enemy's presence!

101
00:09:24,990 --> 00:09:27,210
I can feel your anger!

102
00:09:33,960 --> 00:09:35,800
Damn...

103
00:09:38,460 --> 00:09:39,500
Who's there?

104
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,260
Go away, you guys...

105
00:09:49,520 --> 00:09:51,520
I don't want any food.

106
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:54,940
Rayleigh said I can't eat,
so I won't eat!

107
00:09:58,510 --> 00:10:00,620
Focus, Luffy.

108
00:10:11,570 --> 00:10:13,060
Luffy...

109
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:19,610
It's all part of observation haki, but... You're more
proficient in sensing the feelings of living things.

110
00:10:19,610 --> 00:10:22,130
You probably aren't even aware of this...

111
00:10:22,130 --> 00:10:24,280
Huh? Is that so?

112
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:27,030
But if you have that ability,

113
00:10:27,030 --> 00:10:31,300
I'm sure you'll be able to sense
your opponent's moves, too.

114
00:10:33,720 --> 00:10:34,930
Uh-huh.

115
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:40,570
There are some strong people in this world
capable of seeing a bit into the future.

116
00:10:40,570 --> 00:10:41,820
The future?!

117
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:45,630
What will you do when you face them?

118
00:10:45,630 --> 00:10:49,780
With only two years of training,
you won't gain that ability.

119
00:10:50,360 --> 00:10:51,540
You'll have a rough time.

120
00:10:53,450 --> 00:10:55,910
It depends on what kind of person they are.

121
00:10:55,910 --> 00:11:00,640
What? Your opponent's character?!
Does that matter to you?

122
00:11:00,640 --> 00:11:02,880
I've never thought of it like that.

123
00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:05,130
Of course!

124
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:09,050
You're quite the character.

125
00:11:09,050 --> 00:11:11,760
It matters! Like when I can't escape...

126
00:11:14,470 --> 00:11:17,890
I think you'll have trouble in the future.

127
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:25,610
There's no time for you to rest.

128
00:11:25,610 --> 00:11:26,830
What?

129
00:11:26,830 --> 00:11:30,200
Let's continue the training.
Come with me!

130
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,110
Okay!

131
00:11:35,990 --> 00:11:39,660
I'll teach you everything I can.

132
00:12:15,530 --> 00:12:17,950
Grilled Mochi!

133
00:13:59,870 --> 00:14:03,220
If we get caught, we'll be killed-rero !

134
00:14:04,010 --> 00:14:06,360
We have the cake.

135
00:14:06,360 --> 00:14:09,330
They can't just attack us!

136
00:14:09,330 --> 00:14:11,790
When Prometheus gets that big,

137
00:14:11,790 --> 00:14:14,000
he can't move quickly.

138
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:17,550
We'll reach Liqueur Island soon!

139
00:14:19,900 --> 00:14:25,010
It wasn't hard at all.
All because we fixed the paddles in time.

140
00:14:25,010 --> 00:14:26,950
Good job, guys!

141
00:14:26,950 --> 00:14:29,350
Thanks! That's kind of you!

142
00:14:29,350 --> 00:14:33,460
We'll dump the cake at Liqueur Island
and make our great escape-rero !

143
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:36,090
Yeah, that sounds good.

144
00:14:36,090 --> 00:14:38,010
Not yet.

145
00:14:38,010 --> 00:14:39,240
What's wrong, Chiffon?!

146
00:14:39,920 --> 00:14:42,250
Liqueur Island is too close!

147
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:44,400
Let's lure them to Puffs Island!

148
00:14:44,400 --> 00:14:46,740
Hey! Are you out of your mind?!

149
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:52,120
If Mama eats the cake at Liqueur Island
and comes to, out of her ravenous rampage,

150
00:14:52,140 --> 00:14:57,840
there will still be enough time for her
to catch up to the ship belonging to Nami's group!

151
00:14:57,840 --> 00:15:00,960
So what?!
We've done enough already!

152
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:04,180
We're gonna die! Look!

153
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:07,450
Mama is even hungrier now!

154
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:24,240
I wanna eat it!

155
00:15:30,840 --> 00:15:34,790
I wanna eat it already!

156
00:15:37,310 --> 00:15:40,460
Wedding cake...

157
00:15:40,460 --> 00:15:45,390
I wanna eat it!
I really wanna eat it!

158
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:48,490
Do you understand, Chiffon?

159
00:15:48,490 --> 00:15:49,400
Yes.

160
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:51,290
Let's go to Puffs Island.

161
00:15:51,290 --> 00:15:53,140
You weren't listening!

162
00:15:53,140 --> 00:15:58,400
I'll pay my debt to Straw Hat and the others,
even if it costs me my life!

163
00:15:59,160 --> 00:16:01,610
That's what I have decided!

164
00:16:01,610 --> 00:16:04,300
So I'll go by myself if I have to!

165
00:16:06,950 --> 00:16:11,140
Change course!
We'll head to Puffs Island!

166
00:16:11,140 --> 00:16:12,790
What?!

167
00:16:13,510 --> 00:16:15,830
That's my wife!

168
00:16:15,830 --> 00:16:18,630
I love you even more, Chiffon!

169
00:16:20,460 --> 00:16:22,570
Let's go, guys!

170
00:16:22,570 --> 00:16:26,470
Okay, Father!

171
00:16:26,480 --> 00:16:27,970
I'll see you later.

172
00:16:27,970 --> 00:16:30,030
Be careful, Sanji.

173
00:16:30,030 --> 00:16:30,870
Of course!

174
00:16:30,870 --> 00:16:33,980
D-Don't come close! Stay away! Sanji...

175
00:16:33,980 --> 00:16:35,440
...-san !

176
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:39,790
I'll leave the Sunny in your hands!
We're entering the final stage!

177
00:16:39,790 --> 00:16:40,820
Yeah!

178
00:16:40,820 --> 00:16:43,580
Pudding-chan, take me to Cacao Island.

179
00:16:43,580 --> 00:16:48,660
Don't tell me what to do!
And don't act like a bossy husband!

180
00:16:48,660 --> 00:16:49,930
Sanji!

181
00:16:50,510 --> 00:16:52,130
...-san !

182
00:16:52,130 --> 00:16:54,330
Oh? What was that?

183
00:16:54,330 --> 00:16:55,400
Carrot!

184
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,510
Are you okay now?!

185
00:16:57,510 --> 00:17:01,360
I'm sorry, everyone... I was sleeping.

186
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:05,240
No need to apologize!
You did great, Little Sis!

187
00:17:06,900 --> 00:17:12,190
Can Nekomamushi and Inuarashi do that
when they see the full moon too, Little Sis?

188
00:17:12,190 --> 00:17:13,680
Uh-huh!

189
00:17:13,680 --> 00:17:19,420
Both Master Nekomamushi and Duke Inuarashi
are capable of becoming much stronger than I was!

190
00:17:19,420 --> 00:17:20,970
Really?!

191
00:17:32,830 --> 00:17:36,310
Keep watch and tell me which direction
their attacks come from!

192
00:17:36,310 --> 00:17:37,370
Got it!

193
00:17:37,370 --> 00:17:39,820
No!

194
00:17:53,600 --> 00:17:56,170
I need even more liquid.

195
00:17:57,740 --> 00:18:01,460
You're hurting your own men!
You're going too far!

196
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:05,480
There's no way I'm letting
the Straw Hat crew get away!

197
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:06,800
What's that?!

198
00:18:06,800 --> 00:18:09,700
Is she a giant?

199
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:12,250
Can I see your panties...

200
00:18:12,250 --> 00:18:14,330
Stop it, you pervy skeleton!

201
00:18:16,990 --> 00:18:17,990
It's coming again!

202
00:18:17,990 --> 00:18:19,210
Dodge to the right!

203
00:18:24,490 --> 00:18:26,840
Again, to the right!

204
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:33,390
Jinbe, to the left!

205
00:18:36,800 --> 00:18:38,390
That damn Jinbe!

206
00:18:46,190 --> 00:18:50,530
Stay alert!
I'm depending on your directions!

207
00:18:51,460 --> 00:18:52,840
You can count on us!

208
00:18:52,840 --> 00:18:55,680
Don't worry! I'll take responsibility!

209
00:18:55,680 --> 00:18:59,230
Oh, she became even bigger!

210
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:08,090
Smoothie! This ship can't handle your weight!

211
00:19:08,100 --> 00:19:11,280
This will sink them!

212
00:19:11,900 --> 00:19:12,880
Here it comes!

213
00:19:19,970 --> 00:19:21,970
It's huge!

214
00:19:21,970 --> 00:19:23,820
It'll sink us!

215
00:19:23,820 --> 00:19:26,020
Dodge to the right, Jinbe!

216
00:19:46,290 --> 00:19:49,590
Everyone, hang on tight!

217
00:19:49,590 --> 00:19:52,910
Tch! They're so persistent!

218
00:19:53,660 --> 00:19:55,460
Thank you, Pudding-chan.

219
00:19:55,460 --> 00:19:57,670
You've been a huge help to me.

220
00:19:57,670 --> 00:19:58,840
Cut it out!

221
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:03,400
Move over!
Move over to the edge, Sanji...

222
00:20:03,400 --> 00:20:04,610
...-san !

223
00:20:04,610 --> 00:20:07,140
People will think we're husband and wife!

224
00:20:07,140 --> 00:20:08,180
Who will?

225
00:20:11,970 --> 00:20:13,980
A-Anyway,

226
00:20:13,980 --> 00:20:16,680
is this really gonna work out?!

227
00:20:16,680 --> 00:20:21,070
Luffy's gonna come out
surrounded by fleets and armies.

228
00:20:21,070 --> 00:20:25,530
I will save my captain...
no matter what!

229
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:28,120
What's going on with the mirrors?

230
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:32,040
Minister Oven, we made sure that
they were all disposed of, as you ordered.

231
00:20:32,040 --> 00:20:36,510
Your brothers and sisters are
arriving one after another.

232
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:37,880
Okay.

233
00:20:40,360 --> 00:20:44,890
I can't believe this many members of the family
have assembled here on Cacao Island.

234
00:20:44,890 --> 00:20:48,600
Just how wary
of Straw Hat Luffy are they?!

235
00:20:53,520 --> 00:20:56,110
How many enemies are there?
Tens of thousands?

236
00:20:56,110 --> 00:20:57,690
I think they have less than ten.

237
00:20:57,690 --> 00:21:00,490
What?! I'm gonna take a nap.

238
00:21:00,490 --> 00:21:02,410
Wake me up when something happens!

239
00:21:02,410 --> 00:21:03,360
Yes, sir!

240
00:21:03,360 --> 00:21:06,220
The Worst Generation, huh?

241
00:21:06,220 --> 00:21:10,540
I can't let them have their way anymore,

242
00:21:10,540 --> 00:21:14,500
what with my pride of being
a former sweet commander...

243
00:21:14,500 --> 00:21:18,060
Summoning all of our forces to fight such a small group,

244
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:20,380
brings shame to the name
of Emperor Big Mom.

245
00:21:22,290 --> 00:21:26,300
Or is Straw Hat Luffy that formidable?

246
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:32,780
Are you serious, Big Brother Oven?!

247
00:21:32,850 --> 00:21:34,480
It's like a festival!

248
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:36,320
Looks like fun!

249
00:21:37,780 --> 00:21:42,230
Shut up! I know you guys have nothing better to do!
Just follow the plan.

250
00:21:42,230 --> 00:21:46,170
That damn Straw Hat...
He humiliated us at the tea party.

251
00:21:46,170 --> 00:21:48,530
I'll get revenge by killing him!

252
00:21:48,950 --> 00:21:51,930
When we were deployed
as the enraged army,

253
00:21:51,930 --> 00:21:53,910
we should have killed him...

254
00:21:53,910 --> 00:21:57,870
Then, we wouldn't have failed
at the tea party.

255
00:21:57,870 --> 00:22:03,340
Usually, we can easily discern
an invader's movements...

256
00:22:03,340 --> 00:22:07,010
It's so inconvenient
without the territorial sea slugs!

257
00:22:07,010 --> 00:22:11,220
But our preparations are thorough,
and we still have an hour and a half.

258
00:22:11,220 --> 00:22:15,100
When the time comes, they're finished!

259
00:22:16,160 --> 00:22:20,500
The Straw Hat crew's planned rendezvous at Cacao Island

260
00:22:20,500 --> 00:22:22,530
is approximately one hour away.

261
00:22:32,200 --> 00:22:34,750
What's the matter, Straw Hat?!

262
00:22:35,290 --> 00:22:36,800
Is this...

263
00:22:36,800 --> 00:22:39,050
Yeah, that's right.

264
00:22:39,050 --> 00:22:41,720
...the end?!

265
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:54,900
Okay. I'll take you on.

266
00:22:59,310 --> 00:23:00,780
I'm going to end this!

267
00:23:05,190 --> 00:23:08,040
If you can withstand this...

268
00:23:08,040 --> 00:23:10,580
I have already given you my answer...

269
00:23:28,090 --> 00:23:29,440
This is the end...

270
00:23:29,760 --> 00:23:30,600
Yeah.

271
00:23:35,680 --> 00:23:37,420
Gear Fourth!

272
00:24:24,560 --> 00:24:26,200
Snakeman!

273
00:24:35,030 --> 00:24:38,830
Snakeman?
It's a little different than before.

274
00:24:40,290 --> 00:24:43,660
Your observation haki
sure is something...

275
00:24:44,040 --> 00:24:45,330
That's why I'm using...

276
00:24:46,750 --> 00:24:47,790
something faster!

277
00:24:50,130 --> 00:24:53,610
Why use such a simple attack
at this stage in the fight?

278
00:25:01,350 --> 00:25:03,140
What is going on?

279
00:25:06,810 --> 00:25:09,030
Why is it coming from the side?

280
00:25:10,690 --> 00:25:12,990
What was that?

281
00:25:14,030 --> 00:25:16,340
Where did it come from?!

282
00:25:18,530 --> 00:25:20,150
I'm sure I dodged it!

283
00:25:24,620 --> 00:25:27,120
I see... That's how it works!

284
00:25:30,670 --> 00:25:32,340
Chase him, Python!

285
00:25:33,710 --> 00:25:35,010
It's no use!

286
00:25:36,840 --> 00:25:38,890
It accelerates
even though it's stretching!

287
00:25:41,260 --> 00:25:43,110
Gum-Gum...

288
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:44,810
Jet...

289
00:25:44,810 --> 00:25:47,440
Culverin!

290
00:26:12,860 --> 00:26:15,170
This is far from over!

291
00:26:37,070 --> 00:26:40,760
I'm stronger and faster than you!

292
00:26:42,990 --> 00:26:44,380
Catch up to him!

293
00:27:06,430 --> 00:27:08,400
Diced Mochi!

294
00:27:13,770 --> 00:27:15,650
The mochi is so sticky...

295
00:27:17,070 --> 00:27:18,650
and I can't get it off!

296
00:27:28,660 --> 00:27:30,870
I feel dizzy!

297
00:27:33,710 --> 00:27:35,750
Stop! What are you doing?!

298
00:27:38,840 --> 00:27:40,590
Put me down!

299
00:27:40,590 --> 00:27:43,180
Damn! I can't pull myself apart!

300
00:27:43,720 --> 00:27:46,850
This is the end, Straw Hat!

301
00:28:02,530 --> 00:28:04,280
Dammit!

302
00:28:40,640 --> 00:28:42,190
Damn!

303
00:28:43,520 --> 00:28:44,780
It hurts!

304
00:28:46,020 --> 00:28:47,720
This sucks!

305
00:28:49,780 --> 00:28:51,410
I'm so hungry!

306
00:29:03,420 --> 00:29:05,300
What the hell are you saying?!

307
00:29:05,300 --> 00:29:07,800
I'm saying what's on my mind!

308
00:29:07,800 --> 00:29:09,860
I feel better now!

309
00:29:09,860 --> 00:29:12,660
Fall already, Katakuri!

310
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:14,660
Gum-Gum...

311
00:29:14,660 --> 00:29:17,140
Jet Culverin!

312
00:29:17,140 --> 00:29:18,770
Punch Mochi!

313
00:29:50,010 --> 00:29:52,100
Ow, ow, ow, ow!

314
00:29:53,430 --> 00:29:55,480
Go, Python!

315
00:29:57,640 --> 00:30:00,030
Grilled Mochi!

316
00:30:27,270 --> 00:30:28,080
Damn!

317
00:30:35,520 --> 00:30:36,780
What's next?

318
00:30:40,820 --> 00:30:42,320
How interesting!

319
00:30:42,320 --> 00:30:43,280
Bring it on!

320
00:30:43,280 --> 00:30:44,490
Here I come!

321
00:30:46,660 --> 00:30:48,590
Gum-Gum...

322
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:53,630
Black Mamba!

323
00:31:38,010 --> 00:31:41,220
One more attack
and it'll be over, Straw Hat!

324
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:53,070
I'll take you down
no matter what it takes, Katakuri!

325
00:32:00,700 --> 00:32:01,910
That one again!

326
00:32:01,910 --> 00:32:03,750
I'll put you out of your misery!

327
00:32:03,760 --> 00:32:05,710
I don't need you to!

328
00:32:14,350 --> 00:32:16,280
"Shakky's Rip-off Bar"

329
00:32:20,590 --> 00:32:22,260
Now I remember.

330
00:32:26,010 --> 00:32:29,310
I wonder if Monkey-chan's doing all right.

331
00:32:39,310 --> 00:32:41,910
Rise above it, Luffy...

332
00:32:48,100 --> 00:32:50,120
Gum-Gum...

333
00:32:53,080 --> 00:32:54,870
Diced Mochi!

334
00:32:56,330 --> 00:32:58,480
King Cobra!

335
00:33:02,920 --> 00:33:04,760
You can't get away now!

336
00:33:05,590 --> 00:33:07,260
Go!

